import React from 'react'
import { Segment, Sidebar, Divider,Menu, Header, Button, Grid } from 'semantic-ui-react'

class SidePanelLeft extends React.Component{
    render(){

        return(
         
            <Menu
           
           inverted
           fixed='left'
           vertical
           style={{ background: '#e7e7e7', top: '80px'}}
         >
           
            <Grid centered >
              <Grid.Column width={2}>
                <Menu 
                  fluid
                  vertical
                 inverted
                >
                  <Menu.Item
                    name='Channels'
                    color='black'
                  />
                  <Menu.Item name='NewsFeed'
                    color='black'
                    
                  />
               
                </Menu>
              </Grid.Column>

            </Grid>
             
         </Menu>
       
        )

    }
}

export default SidePanelLeft;
